short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Developer tool for the Quell JavaScript library: https://quell.dev

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quell is an open source, lightweight JavaScript library providing a client- and server-side caching solution and cache invalidation for GraphQL. The Quell Developer Tool is designed to enable developers to easily monitor Quell's client- and server-side caching performance, as well as inspect the server-side (Redis-based) cache, and it includes an all-purpose GraphQL network monitor.
